# Daily Motivation Message Generator

A simple, browser-based application that generates motivational quotes and dynamically changes the background GIF. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project is designed to provide users with a fresh dose of inspiration every time they click the reload button.

## Features

- **Random Quote Generation:**  
  Displays a new quote and author each time you click the reload button.
  
- **Dynamic Background:**  
  Randomly updates the page background with a new GIF to enhance the visual experience.
  
- **Responsive Design:**  
  Optimized for different screen sizes and devices.

- **Clean and Modern UI:**  
  Features a minimalistic design with subtle animations and an aesthetically pleasing layout.

